{"tid":1125052,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有些年輕人...","createTime":"2019-04-25T12:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T12:18:23.000Z","uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3bca4c25d299e00b69d69971d53ddb1390921b","tid":1125052,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"一畢業就到某些大型國企和機關中工作。每天沒什麼事，就是吃飯喝酒，福利好得不了了。<br />\n<br />\n人生還沒有奮鬥過就開始養老，自己的理想被丟在一個，用民脂民膏來享受特權。對於這樣的年輕人，我只想問你四個字：請唔請人？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}